Michael J. Fox Celebrity Activists 
Michael J. Fox is one of the most recognizable figures in Hollywood. His diagnosis of Parkinson's disease has driven him to use his fame to raise awareness of the condition and to try to find a cure. This book highlights his all of his efforts in the fight against this debilitating ailment.


 














