Awards and nominations[edit]




Fox was honoured and received the 2,209th star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame on December 16, 2002.[66]


Canada's Walk of Fame

2000: Inducted, Canada's Walk of Fame[5]

Double Helix Medal

2012: CSHL Double Helix Medal Honoree

Hollywood Walk of Fame

2002: Star on the Walk of Fame – 7021 Hollywood Blvd.[67][68]

Goldene Kamera

2011: Goldene Kamera für Lebenswerk (Lifetime Achievement Award), German film and TV award.[69]

Grammy Awards[70]

2010: Won, Best Spoken Word Album – Always Looking Up: Adventures of An Incurable Optimist

Influential Canadian Expat Award

2009: Awarded "Most Influential Canadian Expat", Canadian Expat Association[71]

Honorary Degrees

