Michael J. Fox





Michael J. Fox Hairstyles





View yourself with
Michael J. Fox
hairstyles. We provide easy "How to style" tips as well as letting you know which hairstyles will match your face shape, hair texture and hair density.





















Short Straight Formal 











Styling Time:

10 minutes


Added:
10th November 2010

1 view





Face Shape Suitability:
Oval, Oblong, Square, and Diamond

Description:
This smooth look is cut short around the back and side to allow the top layers to sit flat for a simple finish. This low-fuss style is great for those looking for a neat and tidy hairdo which takes no time to style. Regular trims is needed to maintain shape. 
 read more.









































