1998: Nominated, Best Actor in a Television Series — Comedy or Musical – Spin City[77]
1999: Nominated, Best Actor in a Television Series — Comedy or Musical – Spin City[78]

Saturn Awards

1985: Won, Best Actor – Back to the Future[79]

Screen Actors Guild Awards[32]

1999: Won, Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Comedy Series – Spin City
2000: Won, Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Comedy Series – Spin City

